Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Pine Prairie Prop. No. 1 of 4 -- 2.00 Mills Continuation - BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText: Village of Pine Prairie Proposition No. 1 of 4
Race.FullText: Shall the Village of Pine Prairie (the "Village") continue to levy a tax of two (2.00) mills on all property subject to taxation within the Village (an estimated $11,195.42 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2021 and ending with the year 2030, for the purpose of maintaining and providing police protection for the Village of Pine Prairie?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Pine Prairie Prop. No. 2 of 4 -- 7.00 Mills Continuation - BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText: Village of Pine Prairie Proposition No. 2 of 4
Race.FullText: Shall the Village of Pine Prairie (the "Village") continue to levy a tax of seven (7.00) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the Village (an estimated $39,183.97 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2021 and ending with the year 2030, for the purpose of maintaining the streets in the Village of Pine Prairie?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Pine Prairie Prop. No. 3 of 4 -- 5.00 Mills Continuation - BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText: Village of Pine Prairie Proposition No. 3 of 4
Race.FullText: Shall the Village of Pine Prairie continue to levy a tax of five (5.00) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the Village (an estimated $27,988.55 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2021 and ending with the year 2030, for the purpose of constructing streets in the Village of Pine Prairie?

Race.SpecificTitle: Village of Pine Prairie Prop. No. 4 of 4 -- 3.00 Mills Continuation - BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText: Village of Pine Prairie Proposition No. 4 of 4
Race.FullText: Shall the Village of Pine Prairie continue to levy a tax of three (3.00) mills on all the property subject to taxation in the Village (an estimated $16,793.13 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of eleven (11) years, beginning with the year 2020 and ending with the year 2030, for the purpose of maintaining and operating the recreational parks in the Village of Pine Prairie?
